Summary.valueString: The document is an auto insurance coverage summary from Contoso Ltd. for Bob Carter, covering the period from March 1, 2021, to September 1, 2021. It includes details of the policy, such as the policy number, coverage limits, and premiums for various types of coverage, including bodily injury liability, property damage liability, uninsured motorist, and underinsured motorist. The document also mentions premium discounts and provides contact information for customer service.
